column100:
Teamleader to packing team 
 It's not a requirement, that you have an education as a gardener. It's a benefit, if you have worked in a greenhouse before.  
 Task: 
 - Packing plants - Distribute tasks to the team - Work in the production in periods, where we are not - packing plants tasks 
 We expect, that you: 
 - speak English - have a driver licens B - meet on time - are physical active 
 Gartneriet Møllerhøj is placed in Stige near Odense. In the nursery we produce different kinds of plants of first quality e.g. Hydrangea and Poinsettia. You will be a part of a good and safe workplace, where we prioritize your welfare. You can see the range and read more about us on www.50008.dk 
 If you want to be a part of the Møllerhøj-team please send an application and a résumé to thomas@50008.dk We are constantly calling for an interview and the position will be filled as soon as possible.
